{"tid":395865,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"是誰令年青人涼薄？ - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2017-09-11T07:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T12:52:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e188ac0b46c79c37276052065c9166d4a8c1f4f2","tid":395865,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T07:43:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20148627&amp;category_guid=vice&amp;sup_id=12187389&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170911\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20148627%26category_guid%3Dvice%26sup_id%3D12187389%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170911&d=zm1YLSEXK%2Bh7fiA9yBSUQRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=db415695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20148627%26category_guid%3Dvice%26sup_id%3D12187389%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170911&h=16b247fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20148627&amp;category_guid=vice&amp;sup_id=12187389&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170911</a><br />\n<br />\n是誰令年青人涼薄？ - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n名采論壇   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170911/large/fung.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170911%2Flarge%2Ffung.jpg&h=30f336f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在教育大學民主牆上張貼「恭喜」者，被一眾社會賢達痛斥「冷血」、「涼薄」，教大校長更直指言論「超越人性道德底線」。人家有喪子之痛，你竟幸災樂禍，道德上當然說不過去。<br />\n<br />\n什麼是道德底線呢？舉個例：上月尾，疑因醫院開漏藥導致肝衰竭的病人鄧桂思去世，我在電視上看見林鄭回應事件，她聲稱「感到非常傷心」，但奇在她說這句話時，氣定神閒，說完後，也像平日般口若懸河，情緒未見絲毫波動。有人死了，至少也得像林鄭那樣講句「非常傷心」，哪怕完全交不到戲，但至少符合校長自訂的「人性道德底線」。<br />\n<br />\n其實講道德沒問題，但要講得徹底、認真，可惜現在很多譴責「涼薄」的人，不見得真的對道德感興趣，反而像法國十七世紀金句王La Rochefoucauld所說：「大家譴責惡行，讚揚美德，不過為了私利。」（On ne bl&acirc;me le vice et on ne loue la vertu que par int&eacute;r&ecirc;t）現在炮轟「涼薄」的賢達，都認為涼薄本身十惡不赦，大家只要把張貼者置諸死地就夠了，至於他為什麼這樣涼薄，並無深究必要。<br />\n<br />\n但真正關心道德和教育問題的人，最應該問「為什麼」。「涼薄」這股unhealthy wind，遠因有羅范椒芬，06年兩位教師疑不堪教改壓力，相繼自殺，時任教統局常任秘書長的羅范回應：「根本上教改有很多學校推行，如果是（與教改有關），為何只有這兩名教師（自殺）呢？」近的有賢達向年青人訓話，意思是你在香港買不起樓、不愛中國，就好行夾唔送吧。多年來，年青人就是聽着達官貴人這些風涼話長大，而他們說了這些話後，依然高官厚祿，沒有後果，也難怪年青人要「見賢思齊」。<br />\n<br />\n孟子說：「上有好者，下必有甚焉者矣。」有涼薄的官，才有涼薄的民，這不是我說的，是孔、孟之道，你是中國人，千萬不要告訴我你不懂中華文化。"},{"pid":"37561d1b5272878e9b016e3a3323fc5ddd8cb531","tid":395865,"uid":42288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc06f43403225987249bc90f77cdbdebf53c9585","tid":395865,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:09:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006360cf2e76820338b6b0e045c5646a8cdc7899","tid":395865,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:22:38.000Z","msg":"unhealthy wind<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出自邊度 好似好熟"},{"pid":"f11bfac5d4e1de51d724cdaf67f77d6f83a308fc","tid":395865,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>unhealthy wind<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出自邊度 好似好熟</blockquote><br />\n狗官"},{"pid":"0c5b464cbb4a7dfd143f0d1b00c97ed02b69531d","tid":395865,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b77e94758be9744e61b5b6b7ad4b516de479e9a","tid":395865,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T12:52:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>unhealthy wind<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出自邊度 好似好熟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n楊生"}]}